## Naming Conventions

| Type | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| ViewModel (AndroidX, feature module) | `*ViewModel` | `SearchFriendViewModel` (thin; forwards to `ScreenModel`) |
| ScreenModel (KMP `:shared:presentation`) | `*ScreenModel` | `SearchFriendScreenModel` |
| UI State | `*UiState` (sealed class) | `SearchFriendUiState` |
| Repository Interface | `*Repository` | `UserRepository` |
| Repository Implementation | `*RepositoryImpl` | `UserRepositoryImpl` |
| Screen (Container) | `*Screen` | `SearchFriendScreen` |
| View (Stateless) | `*View` / `*Content` | `SearchFriendView`, `MyFriendListContent` |
| UI Model | `*UiModel` (shared) or legacy `*UI` / `*Ui` | `SearchFriendUiModel`, `UserCardUI` |
| Activity | `*Activity` | `SearchFriendActivity` |
| Navigator Interface | `*Navigator` | `SearchFriendNavigator` |
| Navigator Implementation | `*NavigatorImpl` | `SearchFriendNavigatorImpl` |
| Koin Module | `*Module` | `dashboardModule` |
| Request Interface | `*Request` | `FriendsRequest` |
| DataStore Interface | `*DataStore` | `FriendsDataStore` |
| DAO | `*Dao` | `FriendsDao` |

